    <div id="modal1" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close-modal" onclick="closeModal('modal1')">&times;</span>
            <h2 style="color: #667eea;">Accelerating Gaming Platform Onboarding</h2>
            
            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Challenge</h3>
            <p>When I joined a leading gaming technology company as Product Owner for Integrations, partner onboarding was taking 8 weeks from contract signing to going live. This created:</p>
            <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Revenue delays for both partners and the business</li>
                <li>Frustrated partners considering competitors</li>
                <li>Constant firefighting and manual intervention</li>
                <li>Engineering team overwhelmed with support tickets</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">My Approach</h3>
            <p><strong>1. Data Analysis First:</strong> I built Power BI dashboards tracking every integration phase, identifying bottlenecks in documentation and technical setup.</p>
            <p><strong>2. Stakeholder Workshops:</strong> Ran sessions with commercial, technical, and operations teams to map the ideal onboarding journey.</p>
            <p><strong>3. Self-Service Framework:</strong> Created standardized documentation, sandbox environments, and automated validation tools.</p>
            <p><strong>4. Iterative Delivery:</strong> Shipped improvements in 2-week sprints, measuring impact after each release.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Results</h3>
            <div class="impact">
                <ul class="impact-list">
                    <li><strong>25% reduction</strong> in onboarding time (8 weeks ‚Üí 6 weeks)</li>
                    <li><strong>100+ weeks saved</strong> collectively across all integrations</li>
                    <li><strong>40% reduction</strong> in support tickets during onboarding</li>
                    <li><strong>Significantly improved</strong> partner satisfaction scores</li>
                    <li>Scaled from 10 to 50+ active integrations without adding headcount</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">Key Learnings</h3>
            <p>The biggest win wasn't the technical improvements - it was aligning stakeholders on <em>why</em> speed mattered and getting buy-in for the investment in self-service tools.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal2" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close-modal" onclick="closeModal('modal2')">&times;</span>
            <h2 style="color: #667eea;">Data-Driven Product Prioritization</h2>
            
            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Challenge</h3>
            <p>Multiple stakeholders (Commercial, Operations, Engineering) were all pushing competing priorities. Roadmap planning meetings turned into hour-long debates with no clear decisions.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">My Solution</h3>
            <p><strong>Created a Prioritization Framework:</strong></p>
            <ul style="margin: 15px 0; padding-left: 20px;">
                <li>Built Power BI dashboard showing: customer requests, revenue impact, implementation effort</li>
                <li>Implemented RICE scoring (Reach, Impact, Confidence, Effort)</li>
                <li>Weekly data review sessions replacing opinion-based debates</li>
                <li>Transparent scoring visible to all stakeholders</li>
            </ul>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Impact</h3>
            <div class="impact">
                <ul class="impact-list">
                    <li>Roadmap alignment meetings reduced from 2 hours to 30 minutes</li>
                    <li>Team velocity increased 20% (less rework, clearer priorities)</li>
                    <li>Stakeholder satisfaction scores improved by XX%</li>
                    <li>Delivered XX high-impact features in 6 months vs XX the previous year</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div id="modal3" class="modal">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <span class="close-modal" onclick="closeModal('modal3')">&times;</span>
            <h2 style="color: #667eea;">Building Self-Service Integration Framework</h2>
            
            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Challenge</h3>
            <p>Partners integrating with our gaming platform required constant support from our engineering and product teams. Common questions like "How do I authenticate?", "Where's the test data?", and "Why is this error happening?" created bottlenecks and slowed onboarding.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">My Approach</h3>
            <p><strong>1. Partner Pain Point Analysis:</strong> Interviewed 10 recent partners to identify where they got stuck most often.</p>
            <p><strong>2. Documentation Overhaul:</strong> Rewrote our API documentation with step-by-step guides, code examples, and troubleshooting sections.</p>
            <p><strong>3. Self-Service Sandbox:</strong> Worked with engineering to improve sandbox environment with realistic test data and automated validation.</p>
            <p><strong>4. Knowledge Base:</strong> Built comprehensive FAQ and video tutorials addressing the top 20 questions we received.</p>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">The Impact</h3>
            <div class="impact">
                <ul class="impact-list">
                    <li><strong>35% reduction</strong> in support tickets during integration phase</li>
                    <li>Partners able to complete sandbox testing <strong>independently</strong> in 90% of cases</li>
                    <li>Support team workload decreased, allowing focus on complex issues</li>
                    <li>Partner feedback: "Clearest API docs we've seen in gaming industry"</li>
                    <li>Framework now serves 50+ partners across multiple jurisdictions</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <h3 style="margin-top: 30px;">Key Learnings</h3>
            <p>The best documentation anticipates questions before partners ask them. Investing time upfront in comprehensive guides pays back 10x in reduced support burden.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openModal(modalId) {
            document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = 'block';
            document.body.style.overflow = 'hidden';
        }

        function closeModal(modalId) {
            document.getElementById(modalId).style.display = 'none';
            document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
        }

        // Close modal when clicking outside
        window.onclick = function(event) {
            if (event.target.classList.contains('modal')) {
                event.target.style.display = 'none';
                document.body.style.overflow = 'auto';
            }
        }
    </script>
